@title SafeMath
 @dev Math operations with safety checks that throw on error.
@dev Returns the multiplication of two unsigned integers, reverting on overflow.
@dev Returns the integer division of two unsigned integers, reverting on division by zero.
@dev Returns the subtraction of two unsigned integers, reverting on overflow (i.e. if subtrahend is greater than minuend).
@dev Returns the addition of two unsigned integers, reverting on overflow.
